🧠 QUESTIONS (ACTUAL DOORDASH-STYLE)

These are very close to what people report on Medium / Glassdoor.

🟢 Q1 — EASY

For each city, find the total number of delivered orders in the last 30 days.

🟡 Q2 — MEDIUM (YOU FOUND THIS) ⭐

Find the top 3 restaurants by revenue in the last 30 days.

Requirements:

Consider only delivered orders

Revenue = sum(order_amount)

Use last 30 days based on order_delivered_ts

🟡 Q3 — MEDIUM

For each restaurant, calculate:

total delivered orders

total revenue
for the last 7 days.

🔴 Q4 — HARD (YOU FOUND THIS) ⭐

Calculate the 90th percentile delivery time per city.

Notes:

Delivery time = order_delivered_ts - order_created_ts

Consider only delivered orders

Percentile must be calculated per city

(Hint: MySQL vs Postgres difference matters here.)

🟡 Q5 — MEDIUM

For each city and day, calculate the average delivery time.

